As an office worker, I want to set up to-do items,
    so that I may plan out my tasks for the work day.

As a student, I want to build a to-do list,
    so that I may be more in control in completing my assignments
    in a timely manner.

As a manager, I want to create a to-do list,
    so that it may support my business's plan of action in meeting
    their short-term and long-term goals.